<P>_BY this time it was waxe~ euen dark night and our Hoa&s;t &s;peaking vnto <HI>Pierce</HI> &s;aid vnto him Neighbour <HI>Pierce</HI> (quoth h&eacute;e) w&eacute;e haue rea|&s;oned &s;o very long to and fro that the night is &s;tolen vpon vs, and the purpo&s;e of your com|ming hither vtterly forgoten through our ear+ne&s;t di&s;putation in the&s;e matters.</P>
