<LG>
<L>_THus ended is this &s;horte Collection,</L>
<L>Rude and vnperfect for his want of &s;ki<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="KEYERS" EXTENT="1 letter">&punc;</L>
<L>Who &s;hould haue giuen it perfection,</L>
<L>and would, if his might had been to his wil</L>
